    {
      "lineNumber": 3,
      "text": "Conferences with AFIC, notification of government officials in responsible positions",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 4,
      "text": "Conferences with CIA; DOR clouds and effects, DOR removal (Smog so-called,",
      "status": "permanent_unresolved",
      "unresolvedReason": "other_documented"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 5,
      "text": "also appears as smoky substance subsequent to UFO sightings as you know); DOR",
      "status": "permanent_unresolved",
      "unresolvedReason": "other_documented"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 6,
      "text": "as Deadly Orgone Energy ; Orone ; Oranur Weather control ; Rainmaking, also",
      "status": "permanent_unresolved",
      "unresolvedReason": "other_documented"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 7,
      "text": "over deserts, Hurricane dissipation; Transportation of Orur including squeezing",
      "status": "permanent_unresolved",
      "unresolvedReason": "other_documented"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 8,
      "text": "of Radar, ; Breakdown (Hemiplegia) of spacegun operator while drawing from Ra,",
      "status": "permanent_unresolved",
      "unresolvedReason": "other_documented"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 9,
      "text": "And many further detailed aspects of OROP Desert Ra work such as the \"energetic",
      "status": "permanent_unresolved",
      "unresolvedReason": "other_documented"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 10,
      "text": "nodes found experimentally\", etc., etc.... There is no shortage of facts",
      "status": "permanent_unresolved",
      "unresolvedReason": "other_documented"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 11,
      "text": "observations, and evidence. But the Truth has so far not yet been heard, which",
      "status": "permanent_unresolved",
      "unresolvedReason": "other_documented"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 12,
      "text": "is all it needs to win.",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 13,
      "status": "blank"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 14,
      "text": "Furthermore there is evidence for espionage against this work ; Tapped",
      "status": "permanent_unresolved",
      "unresolvedReason": "other_documented"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 15,
      "text": "radio, opened mail etc. Since to date UFO's are officially \"nonexistent\"",
      "status": "permanent_unresolved",
      "unresolvedReason": "other_documented"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 16,
      "text": "the FBI has sofar declined to investigate as the subject is \"not within their",
      "status": "permanent_unresolved",
      "unresolvedReason": "other_documented"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 17,
      "text": "jurisdiction\". I am personally witness to the fact of the existence of",
      "status": "permanent_unresolved",
      "unresolvedReason": "other_documented"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 18,
      "text": "the Orgone Energy Motor, and letters, documents, etc., describing the",
      "status": "permanent_unresolved",
      "unresolvedReason": "other_documented"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 19,
      "text": "mysterious disappearance of one William Washington who came into possession",
      "status": "permanent_unresolved",
      "unresolvedReason": "other_documented"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 20,
      "text": "of much knowledge concerning \"orgonometry, mathematical, and the Motor principle",
      "status": "permanent_unresolved",
      "unresolvedReason": "other_documented"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 21,
      "text": "and who has disappeared since 1949. I am sure any investigating agency could",
      "status": "permanent_unresolved",
      "unresolvedReason": "other_documented"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 22,
      "text": "locate his whereabouts in a short time. It is clear that the powerful",
      "status": "permanent_unresolved",
      "unresolvedReason": "other_documented"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 23,
      "text": "Oil interests in this country are out to keep their predominance in the field",
      "status": "permanent_unresolved",
      "unresolvedReason": "other_documented"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 24,
      "text": "of power and income, and are involved in keeping the Orgone Energy Motor",
      "status": "permanent_unresolved",
      "unresolvedReason": "other_documented"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 25,
      "text": "problem suppressed.",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 26,
      "status": "blank"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 27,
      "text": "These points are mentioned to give you a hint how necessary a bona fide,",
      "status": "permanent_unresolved",
      "unresolvedReason": "other_documented"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 28,
      "text": "courageous, forthright investigation has become. I am appending a bibliography",
      "status": "permanent_unresolved",
      "unresolvedReason": "other_documented"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 29,
      "text": "for your convenience where you may find some of the printed evidence for our",
      "status": "permanent_unresolved",
      "unresolvedReason": "other_documented"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 30,
      "text": "charges.",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 31,
      "status": "blank"
    },
    {
